---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Lagless.gg: Reliable Gaming Infrastructure — Case Study | Nelexa"
  description="How Nelexa provided hardware, colocation, and networking solutions for Lagless.gg's gaming servers."
>
  <article class="bg-black">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-36 pb-14 bg-black overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[900px] h-[400px] bg-primary-800/25 rounded-full blur-[140px] pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-bg opacity-30"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 border border-primary-500/30 text-primary-300 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Colocation</span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 border border-primary-500/30 text-primary-300 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">IP Transit</span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 border border-primary-500/30 text-primary-300 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">Hardware Solutions</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white mb-6">
            Lagless.gg: <span class="gradient-text italic">Reliable Gaming Infrastructure</span>
          </h1>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/50">
            <span class="font-semibold text-white">Lagless.gg</span> · January 15, 2024 · 3 min read
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Body -->
    <section class="relative py-14 bg-black">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-lg prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-headings:text-white prose-p:text-white/70 prose-li:text-white/70 prose-strong:text-white prose-a:text-primary-400 hover:prose-a:text-primary-300">
          <h2>The Challenge</h2>
          <p>Lagless.gg was starting from scratch. They had an idea for a gaming hosting service but no infrastructure to support it. They needed everything — servers, data center space, and reliable internet connections to get their business off the ground.</p>

          <h2>The Solution</h2>
          <p>Nelexa built Lagless.gg's entire infrastructure from the ground up:</p>
          <p><strong>Hardware Solutions</strong> — We provided high-performance servers optimized for gaming workloads. These servers can handle multiple game instances and provide the processing power needed for smooth gameplay.</p>
          <p><strong>Colocation Services</strong> — We secured data center space with proper power, cooling, and security. This gives Lagless.gg a professional hosting environment without the massive upfront costs of building their own facility.</p>
          <p><strong>Networking Solutions</strong> — We set up fast, reliable internet connections with low latency. This ensures players get good ping times and stable connections during gameplay.</p>

          <h2>The Results</h2>
          <p>With Nelexa's infrastructure, Lagless.gg was able to launch their gaming hosting service successfully. Their servers run smoothly with reliable uptime, and their customers get the performance they need for competitive gaming.</p>

          <h2>What the Team Says</h2>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-6 italic text-white/80 text-xl leading-relaxed">
            "Nelexa built our entire infrastructure from nothing. We came to them with just an idea and they provided everything we needed — servers, data center space, and networking. It's been reliable and cost-effective for our gaming servers. The colocation and networking solutions work perfectly for our needs."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-sm not-italic">— Alex Chatham, CTO</p>

          <p><em>Need reliable infrastructure for your gaming servers? <a href="/contact">Contact Nelexa</a> for hardware, colocation, and networking solutions.</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-black border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="relative glass-card overflow-hidden p-10 md:p-14 text-center">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600/15 to-accent-700/10"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-white mb-4">Ready to achieve similar results?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Let our enterprise infrastructure experts help you implement similar solutions for your organization. Contact us to discuss your specific requirements.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
              <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-xl shadow-primary-900/40">Get Custom Solution</a>
              <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">View More Case Studies</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
